MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

97-2477. State ex rel. Wheeler v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 96APD09-1207. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the application for dismissal of appellants, Industrial Commission of Ohio and Bureau of Workers’ Compensation,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted. The appeal of Metro Electric, Inc. remains pending.
